Record Class ExpressionWithContext

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
io.micronaut.expressions.context.ExpressionWithContext
Record Components:
expressionReference - reference to evaluated expression in annotation

@Internal public record ExpressionWithContext(@NonNull EvaluatedExpressionReference expressionReference, @NonNull ExpressionCompilationContext evaluationContext) extends Record
